description: Pristine South Boston PENTHOUSE! This property has not seen the market in over a decade. A+ location just steps to the beach, Castle Island, and bus stops on Broadway. This charming unit was gut renovated in 2009, with new roof installed in 2014. Comes equipped with Central AC, granite/stainless kitchen, hardwood floors, and terrific natural light. Spacious bedroom with large closet. Bathroom is over-sized with in-unit laundry as well. Pet friendly building with high owner occupancy -- just moments to shops, restaurants, public transportation, and highway access. Easy on-street parking, w/ ROOF RIGHTS, LOW TAXES & LOW CONDO FEE. This one won't last long!
